{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":886,"text":"I love museums."},{"time":4480,"text":"Have you guys ever been\nto the Natural History Museum?"},{"time":7040,"text":"In New York City?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":8480,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":10160,"text":"So one of the things that I do\nis I take my kids to the museum."},{"time":15880,"text":"Recently I took them\nto the Natural History Museum."},{"time":18480,"text":"I had my two sons with me,\nSabian and Dabith."},{"time":21640,"text":"And we go into the front\nentrance of the museum,"},{"time":24280,"text":"and there's that amazing sculpture\nof Teddy Roosevelt out there."},{"time":27936,"text":"You guys know which one I'm talking about."},{"time":29960,"text":"Teddy Roosevelt is sitting there\nwith one hand on the horse,"},{"time":33080,"text":"bold, strong, sleeves rolled up."},{"time":35440,"text":"I don't know if he's bare-chested,\nbut it kind of feels like it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38480,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":39840,"text":"And on the left-hand side of him\nis a Native American walking."},{"time":44520,"text":"And on the right-hand side of him\nis an African-American walking."},{"time":49720,"text":"And as we're moving up the stairs,"},{"time":53200,"text":"getting closer to the sculpture,"},{"time":56160,"text":"my oldest son, who's nine, says,"},{"time":58240,"text":"\"Dad, how come he gets to ride,"},{"time":63120,"text":"and they have to walk?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":66440,"text":"It stopped me in my tracks."},{"time":68520,"text":"It stopped me in my tracks."},{"time":70600,"text":"There was so much history"},{"time":72080,"text":"that we would have to go through\nto try to explain that,"},{"time":74760,"text":"and that's something\nI try to do with them anyways."},{"time":78440,"text":"It's a question that I probably\nwould have never really asked."},{"time":82720,"text":"But fundamentally what he was saying was,"},{"time":84920,"text":"\"That doesn't look fair."},{"time":86720,"text":"Dad, that doesn't look fair."},{"time":89040,"text":"And why is this thing that's so not fair"},{"time":91640,"text":"sitting outside\nof such an amazing institution.\""},{"time":95640,"text":"And his question got me wondering,"},{"time":97320,"text":"is there a way for us\nto amend our public sculptures,"},{"time":102200,"text":"our national monuments?"},{"time":104320,"text":"Not erase them,"},{"time":106320,"text":"but is there a way to amend them?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":108600,"text":"Now, I didn't grow up going to museums."},{"time":113080,"text":"That's not my history."},{"time":115440,"text":"My mother was 15 years old\nwhen I was born."},{"time":117640,"text":"She is amazing."},{"time":120120,"text":"My father was struggling\nwith his own things"},{"time":122480,"text":"for most of my life."},{"time":125840,"text":"If you really want to know the truth,"},{"time":127880,"text":"the only reason I got into art\nis because of a woman."},{"time":131960,"text":"There was this amazing, amazing,\nfantastic, beautiful, smart woman,"},{"time":136840,"text":"four years older than me,"},{"time":138200,"text":"and I wanted to go out with her."},{"time":140040,"text":"But she said, \"You're too young"},{"time":141560,"text":"and you're not thinking\nabout your future.\""},{"time":143800,"text":"So I ran on down to the junior college,"},{"time":147480,"text":"registered for some classes,"},{"time":149680,"text":"ran on back,"},{"time":151360,"text":"and basically was like,\n\"I'm thinking about my future now.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":154200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":156640,"text":"\"Can we go out?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":159080,"text":"For the record, she's even more amazing."},{"time":161520,"text":"I married her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162760,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":168360,"text":"So when I randomly ran down\nto the junior college"},{"time":173040,"text":"and registered for classes,"},{"time":174440,"text":"I really wasn't paying attention\nto what I was registering to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":178160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":179440,"text":"So I ended up with an art history class,"},{"time":182200,"text":"and I didn't know a thing\nabout art history."},{"time":185440,"text":"But something amazing happened\nwhen I went into that class."},{"time":189680,"text":"For the first time in my academic career,"},{"time":193520,"text":"my visual intelligence was required of me."},{"time":196920,"text":"For the first time."},{"time":198560,"text":"The professor would put up an image,"},{"time":200640,"text":"bold strokes of blues and yellows,\nand say, \"Who's that?\""},{"time":204800,"text":"And I'd go, \"That's Van Gogh.\nClearly that is Van Gogh."},{"time":207720,"text":"I got this.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":209320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":211280,"text":"I got a B in that class."},{"time":214240,"text":"For me, that was amazing."},{"time":218360,"text":"In high school, let's just say\nI wasn't a great student. OK?"},{"time":222680,"text":"In high school, my GPA was .65."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225120,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":226640,"text":"Decimal point first, six five."},{"time":230960,"text":"So me getting a B was huge, huge,"},{"time":235120,"text":"absolutely huge."},{"time":236880,"text":"And because of the fact that I realized\nthat I was able to learn things visually"},{"time":241840,"text":"that I couldn't learn in other ways,"},{"time":243600,"text":"this became my strategy,\nthis became my tactic"},{"time":246480,"text":"for understanding everything else."},{"time":249760,"text":"I wanted to stay in this relationship.\nThings were going well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252720,"text":"I decided, let me keep taking\nthese art history classes."},{"time":255400,"text":"One of the last art history classes,\nI will not forget, I will never forget."},{"time":259000,"text":"It was one of those survey\nart history classes."},{"time":261240,"text":"Anybody ever have one of those\nsurvey art history classes,"},{"time":264000,"text":"where they try to teach you\nthe entire history of art"},{"time":266960,"text":"in a single semester?"},{"time":268440,"text":"I'm talking about cave paintings\nand Jackson Pollock"},{"time":273480,"text":"just crunched together all in the same --"},{"time":275760,"text":"It doesn't really work,\nbut they try anyway."},{"time":279680,"text":"Well, at the beginning of the semester,"},{"time":282200,"text":"I looked at the book,"},{"time":283440,"text":"and in this 400-page book\nwas about a 14-page section"},{"time":287400,"text":"that was on black people in painting."},{"time":289520,"text":"Now, this was a crammed in section"},{"time":291560,"text":"that had representations\nof black people in painting"},{"time":295960,"text":"and black people who painted."},{"time":298720,"text":"It was poorly curated,\nlet's just put it that way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":303040,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":304280,"text":"Nonetheless I was really excited about it,"},{"time":307640,"text":"because in all\nthe other classes that I had,"},{"time":309960,"text":"we didn't even have that conversation."},{"time":313120,"text":"We didn't talk about it at all."},{"time":315720,"text":"So imagine my surprise"},{"time":317480,"text":"when I get to class"},{"time":319080,"text":"and on the day that we're supposed\nto go over that particular chapter,"},{"time":323320,"text":"my professor announces,"},{"time":326160,"text":"\"We're going to skip this chapter today"},{"time":328080,"text":"because we do not have time\nto go through it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":330840,"text":"\"Whoa, I'm sorry,\nhold on, professor, professor."},{"time":333720,"text":"I'm sorry. This is a really\nimportant chapter to me."},{"time":337320,"text":"Are we going to go over it at any point?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":339600,"text":"\"Titus, we don't have time for this.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":341440,"text":"\"I'm sorry, I'm sorry,\nI'm sorry, I'm sorry,"},{"time":343560,"text":"please, I really need to understand."},{"time":345320,"text":"Clearly the author thinks\nthat this is significant."},{"time":347760,"text":"Why are we skipping over this?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":349320,"text":"\"Titus, I do not have time for this.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":351360,"text":"\"OK, last question, I'm really sorry here."},{"time":353640,"text":"When can we talk,\nbecause we need to talk.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":355720,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":357560,"text":"I went to her office hours."},{"time":359800,"text":"I ended up getting kicked\nout of her office."},{"time":362360,"text":"I went to the dean."},{"time":363880,"text":"The dean finally told me,\n\"I can't force her to teach anything.\""},{"time":366960,"text":"And I knew in that moment\nif I wanted to understand this history,"},{"time":371040,"text":"if I wanted to understand the roles\nof those folks who had to walk,"},{"time":375480,"text":"I was probably going\nto have to figure that out myself."},{"time":381600,"text":"So ..."},{"time":387960,"text":"above you right here on the slide"},{"time":391320,"text":"is a painting by Frans Hals."},{"time":395200,"text":"This is one of the kinds of images"},{"time":399960,"text":"that was in that chapter."},{"time":403320,"text":"I taught myself how to paint"},{"time":405440,"text":"by going to museums\nand looking at images like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411640,"text":"I want to show you something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":426120,"text":"I made this."},{"time":428320,"text":"I --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":429560,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":431000,"text":"I made some alterations."},{"time":432280,"text":"You'll see there are\nsome slight differences in the painting."},{"time":436840,"text":"All this art history\nthat I had been absorbing"},{"time":441560,"text":"helped me to realize\nthat painting is a language."},{"time":449280,"text":"There is a reason"},{"time":455840,"text":"why he is the highest\nin the composition here."},{"time":465800,"text":"There is a reason"},{"time":469560,"text":"why the painter is showing us\nthis gold necklace here."},{"time":476640,"text":"He's trying to tell us something\nabout the economic status"},{"time":479400,"text":"of these people in these paintings."},{"time":484320,"text":"Painting is a visual language"},{"time":488280,"text":"where everything in the painting"},{"time":491800,"text":"is meaningful, is important."},{"time":494520,"text":"It's coded."},{"time":500600,"text":"But sometimes, because\nof the compositional structure,"},{"time":503720,"text":"because of compositional hierarchy,"},{"time":506440,"text":"it's hard to see other things."},{"time":524320,"text":"This silk is supposed to tell us also\nthat they have quite a bit of money."},{"time":530840,"text":"There's more written"},{"time":532520,"text":"about dogs in art history"},{"time":536520,"text":"than there are about\nthis other character here."},{"time":541200,"text":"Historically speaking,\nin research on these kinds of paintings,"},{"time":544320,"text":"I can find out more about the lace"},{"time":548320,"text":"that the woman is wearing\nin this painting --"},{"time":551320,"text":"the manufacturer of the lace --\nthan I can about this character here,"},{"time":556080,"text":"about his dreams, about his hopes,"},{"time":558240,"text":"about what he wanted out of life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":563280,"text":"I want to show you something."},{"time":567200,"text":"I don't want you to think"},{"time":569080,"text":"that this is about eradication."},{"time":573040,"text":"It's not."},{"time":574280,"text":"The oil that you saw me\njust put inside of this paint"},{"time":578440,"text":"is linseed oil."},{"time":579960,"text":"It becomes transparent over time,"},{"time":582800,"text":"so eventually what's going to happen"},{"time":585880,"text":"is these faces"},{"time":588320,"text":"will emerge a little bit."},{"time":592400,"text":"What I'm trying to do,"},{"time":594320,"text":"what I'm trying to show you,"},{"time":596400,"text":"is how to shift your gaze just slightly,"},{"time":599800,"text":"just momentarily,"},{"time":601720,"text":"just momentarily,"},{"time":603160,"text":"to ask yourself the question,"},{"time":606360,"text":"why do some have to walk?"},{"time":608360,"text":"What is the impact of these kinds\nof sculptures at museums?"},{"time":612640,"text":"What is the impact\nof these kinds of paintings"},{"time":616240,"text":"on some of our most vulnerable in society,"},{"time":619160,"text":"seeing these kinds of depictions\nof themselves all the time?"},{"time":623160,"text":"I'm not saying erase it."},{"time":625000,"text":"We can't erase this history."},{"time":627200,"text":"It's real. We have to know it."},{"time":629880,"text":"I think of it in the same way"},{"time":631840,"text":"we think of --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":635760,"text":"Let me step back a second."},{"time":637880,"text":"You remember old-school cameras,"},{"time":640240,"text":"where when you took a picture,\nyou actually had to focus. Right?"},{"time":643560,"text":"You'd put the camera up,"},{"time":644840,"text":"and if I wanted you in focus,"},{"time":646840,"text":"I would move the lens a little to the left"},{"time":648864,"text":"and you would come forward."},{"time":650200,"text":"I could move the lens\na little to the right,"},{"time":652320,"text":"and you would go back and the folks\nin the background would come out."},{"time":655600,"text":"I'm just trying to do that here."},{"time":657640,"text":"I'm trying to give you that opportunity."},{"time":661240,"text":"I'm trying to answer that question"},{"time":663480,"text":"that my son had."},{"time":668080,"text":"I want to make paintings,"},{"time":670080,"text":"I want to make sculptures"},{"time":672360,"text":"that are honest,"},{"time":674600,"text":"that wrestle with\nthe struggles of our past"},{"time":679400,"text":"but speak to the diversity\nand the advances of our present."},{"time":684880,"text":"And we can't do that by taking an eraser\nand getting rid of stuff."},{"time":688080,"text":"That's just not going to work."},{"time":689840,"text":"I think that we should\ndo it in the same way"},{"time":691960,"text":"the American Constitution works."},{"time":693560,"text":"When we have a situation"},{"time":694840,"text":"where we want to change\na law in the American Constitution,"},{"time":698720,"text":"we don't erase the other one."},{"time":701520,"text":"Alongside that is an amendment,"},{"time":703760,"text":"something that says,"},{"time":705040,"text":"\"This is where we were,\nbut this is where we are right now.\""},{"time":709440,"text":"I figure if we can do that,"},{"time":711920,"text":"then that will help us\nunderstand a little bit"},{"time":714280,"text":"about where we're going."}]},{"cues":[{"time":746480,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":747720,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}